wikipedia_page.main: Lauren May Hemp (born 7 August 2000) is an English footballer who plays as a forward for FA WSL club Manchester City. She was named England Young Player of the Year in September 2017 and PFA Women's Young Player of the Year in 2018 and 2020.

link_mentions.page: PFA Women's Young Player of the Year
response: The current holder is Lauren Hemp of Manchester City.
